message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your needs and expectations. Given its high value and quality, I understand it might seem expensive at first glance. However, considering its worth to you, I propose we discuss a fair price that reflects its true value while ensuring it's within your budgetary considerations. Would you be open to exploring a negotiation or discussing a price that could make this opportunity more appealing to both of us?
